expression: self_healing_popup
---
  Config: Self-healing
  Automatic recovery from usage and model availability errors.

  Search Self-healing settings
› [ ] Automatic recovery        Retry selected recoverable errors automatically.
  [*] Retry usage limits        Retry after the usage limit reset time when available.
  [*] Retry model capacity      Retry the current model when it is temporarily at
                                capacity.
  [ ] Switch model on capacity  Try another compatible model before retrying a capacity
                                error.
  Back to sections              Return to the config section menu.

  Press space to toggle; esc to close
